  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/742510/extras/8287abf5f7fd6c4dc867af85884e5b45.avif?t=1621769457\" width=609 height=249 /></span><br><br><strong>Explore multiple dimensions in a psychedelic world.</strong> Solve puzzles and overcome obstacles on gravity-defying platforms.<br><br><strong>Welcome to trippy world of Psikodelya!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/742510/extras/28fffc86ec7422ae833d20ca0adf923f.webp?t=1621769457\" width=609 height=32 /></span><br><br>Psikodelya is a first-person puzzle game designed for the player to explore the surrounding world.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/742510/extras/6bd9407f08eb5ecd993a1c2bf415ab13.webp?t=1621769457\" width=609 height=32 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Original Psychedelic Soundtrack<br></li><li> Explore surreal worlds<br></li><li> Puzzles<br></li><li> Gravity-defying Platforms<br></li><li> Psychedelic Experience<br></li><li> Trippy Game</li></ul><br><br><br><i>Photosensitive epileptic seizures warning! A small percentage of people may experience a seizure when exposed to certain visual images, including flashing lights or patterns that appear in videogames.</i>",
